This method body should be only executed when cluster version is >= 4.1, otherwise it might introduce trouble with rolling upgrades. So something like:
if (nodeEngine.getClusterService().getClusterVersion().isGreaterOrEqual(Versions.V4_1)) {
  ... // do stuff
}

edit (note to self): reconsider, maybe old members just ignore the flag they don't know how to deal with

